00:39:58.940 --> 00:40:02.530
or presenting some sort of
utopian view for the Brazilians,

00:40:02.530 --> 00:40:04.770
because so much of what
he says is associated

00:40:04.770 --> 00:40:09.300
with actually fear and,
right, and he's running

00:40:09.300 --> 00:40:14.830
through this fear and that's
