00:40:41.480 --> 00:40:44.940
because these utopias are
actually rethinking core

00:40:44.940 --> 00:40:53.200
problems of the country, which
are inequality, racial injustice

00:40:53.200 --> 00:40:54.500
and so on and so forth.

00:40:54.500 --> 00:40:58.180
So, we always feel
like it's falling short

00:40:58.180 --> 00:41:00.780
