like a poignant example of that,

00:42:07.000 --> 00:42:09.840
but you can see it in
other ones as well.

00:42:09.840 --> 00:42:12.640
I mean, and the idea of
coming together that you see

00:42:12.640 --> 00:42:15.530
in Macunaima, the
ideas of community

00:42:15.530 --> 00:42:17.460
and the [inaudible]
community, it's also there.

00:42:17.460 --> 00:42:21.020
So, if there is a disconnect
