00:42:57.180 --> 00:43:01.180
I think he really
embodies many of the ideas

00:43:01.180 --> 00:43:05.450
that have been latent in Brazil
throughout -- for centuries.

00:43:05.450 --> 00:43:08.910
Again, the fact that he
presents himself as a savior

00:43:08.910 --> 00:43:11.600
of the country, who is
going to bring stability,

00:43:11.600 --> 00:43:13.990
peace, prosperity and so on.

00:43:13.990 --> 00:43:18.860
This was a discourse, messianic
discourse that has been part

00:43:18.860 --> 00:43:23.350
of Brazil for centuries
and is described very well

00:43:23.350 --> 00:43:26.840
by [inaudible] in the
Back Lands when he talks

00:43:26.840 --> 00:43:29.910
about Antonio [inaudible]
and why people voted for him.

00:43:29.910 --> 00:43:34.350
I mean, it's shocking,
but people in many

00:43:34.350 --> 00:43:40.220
of the Brazilian slums or
villas, he won, so the people

00:43:40.220 --> 00:43:42.060
that are going to
be more impacted

00:43:42.060 --> 00:43:45.440
by his policies are
voting for him exactly

00:43:45.440 --> 00:43:50.980
because he has been very
clever at appropriating some

00:43:50.980 --> 00:43:54.260
of these cultural tropes, some
of these cultural themes are

00:43:54.260 --> 00:43:56.530
that are so much part
of Brazilian history

00:43:56.530 --> 00:43:59.710
and of the way Brazilians
think about themselves.

00:43:59.710 --> 00:44:02.710
And I think this is why
he has been so successful.

00:44:02.710 --> 00:44:06.800
And, on the other hand, he has
also capitalized on this feeling

00:44:06.800 --> 00:44:11.080
of discontent that is
also, as I was saying,

00:44:11.080 --> 00:44:15.490
also comes out of this idea
that you're never able to live

00:44:15.490 --> 00:44:18.260
up to the utopian promise
as a Brazilian purpose.

00:44:18.260 --> 00:44:22.200
And, so, you're always
falling short

00:44:22.200 --> 00:44:23.940
and he has capitalized on this.

00:44:23.940 --> 00:44:26.170
He's saying, "I'm
going to overcome this,

00:44:26.170 --> 00:44:29.040
we will not fall short
of Brazil's promise,

00:44:29.040 --> 00:44:31.440
but we will tackle
these problems

00:44:31.440 --> 00:44:33.200
and we will overcome them."

00:44:33.200 --> 00:44:37.540
