00:44:50.070 --> 00:44:53.860
that have been very
prevalent in Brazilian thought

00:44:53.860 --> 00:44:56.110
and he has used them to
his advantage in a way

00:44:56.110 --> 00:44:58.700
that I think the left
has been unable to do

00:44:58.700 --> 00:45:00.490
and that's why he won.

00:45:00.490 --> 00:45:03.730
