00:54:04.360 --> 00:54:09.640
&gt;&gt; How is utopian is the
[inaudible] and shared labor

00:54:09.640 --> 00:54:14.450
and that sort of thing,
how do you then [inaudible]

00:54:14.450 --> 00:54:16.400
with authoritarian control?

00:54:16.400 --> 00:54:21.860
I mean, how was he able
to create this narrative,

00:54:21.860 --> 00:54:31.710
is it simply just harkening
back to the good old days or --

00:54:31.710 --> 00:54:35.600
because I always thought it
had to have this future goal?

00:54:35.600 --> 00:54:38.140
