00:59:18.810 --> 00:59:21.010
&gt;&gt; Patricia Vieira: Yeah,
that's a great question

00:59:21.010 --> 00:59:25.380
and I think that's the main
criticism against utopia

00:59:25.380 --> 00:59:28.530
and the argument that
utopia sometimes leads

00:59:28.530 --> 00:59:31.620
to authoritarianism
goes back to that.

00:59:31.620 --> 00:59:35.990
